arget=\"_blank\">https://www.tonymacx86.com/buyersguide/february/2017#Motherboards</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買唔到980TI,想問呢張1070好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n底板唔得，hackintosh最好Z170/H170</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c6e6f127bce26b08e71e4dba2c244350c2c77b","tid":117372,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"hackintosh咪用gtx10xx，冇hackintosh driver"},{"pid":"c20026c15c8e046946ccb508b3e216d239e95db1","tid":117372,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"MB換Gigabyte GA-Z170X-UD5<br />\n或者Z170X gaming 5<br />\n呢兩塊o唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c3c161465dced61c218d360a28a207e2bf0c94","tid":117372,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hackintosh咪用gtx10xx，冇hackintosh driver</blockquote><br />\n我知啊但問咗好多間都話冇980ti<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住eject顯示卡咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2808ef306f2f285eda5eec0a60a409fe7900542","tid":117372,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"如果你唔係買完要即刻用Hackintosh,可以全部都用新野<br />\n網上好似有人已經成功用Z270底板行Hackintosh,所以你可以睇下點做<br />\n<br />\n順便講,同樣咁多錢我會傾向選擇i7+GTX1060 6GB多過i5+GTX1070<br />\n因為打機i5 CPU好容易唔夠用,好多game已經食到4C8T<br />\nGTX1060 6GB反而多數人都覺得夠<br />\n再有錢可以i7+GTX1070<br />\n<br />\n如果你要買980Ti,去二手市場例如DCFever可能比較容易搵<br />\n用980Ti嘅話火牛最少上RM550x<br />\n<br />\n第時upgrade,換CPU個步驟好繁複,又怕唔小心整到socket彎針<br />\n反而你顯示卡差少少,第時upgrade換過張,個步驟同換CPU比真係容易好多"},{"pid":"78f2bc0c2b19616b4a897255ec0e66a142cfc297","tid":117372,"uid":6386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"EVGA GeForce GTX 980 Ti Super Clocked Gaming ACX 2.0 6GB GDDR5 384bit PCI-E Graphic Card (06G-P4-4995-KR) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00YDAYOK0/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_eAiOybYYJJ2YV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB00YDAYOK0%2Fref%3Dcm_sw_r_cp_api_eAiOybYYJJ2YV&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=09d6c5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00YDAYOK0/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_eAiOybYYJJ2YV</a>"},{"pid":"98744a5bb62a15cd81e8fe47ee85d751f4d6f3e3","tid":117372,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>EVGA GeForce GTX 980 Ti Super Clocked Gaming ACX 2.0 6GB GDDR5 384bit PCI-E Graphic Card (06G-P4-4995-KR) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00YDAYOK0/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_eAiOybYYJJ2YV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB00YDAYOK0%2Fref%3Dcm_sw_r_cp_api_eAiOybYYJJ2YV&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=09d6c5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00YDAYOK0/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_eAiOybYYJJ2YV</a></blockquote><br />\n5000蚊我買1080放棄macos好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw thank you"},{"pid":"7a7e2774701ba3f88cc352f646a3ce92eaaeb3b0","tid":117372,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你唔係買完要即刻用Hackintosh,可以全部都用新野<br />\n網上好似有人已經成功用Z270底板行Hackintosh,所以你可以睇下點做<br />\n<br />\n順便講,同樣咁多錢我會傾向選擇i7+GTX1060 6GB多過i5+GTX1070<br />\n因為打機i5 CPU好容易唔夠用,好多game已經食到4C8T<br />\nGTX1060 6GB反而多數人都覺得夠<br />\n再有錢可以i7+GTX1070<br />\n<br />\n如果你要買980Ti,去二手市場例如DCFever可能比較容易搵<br />\n用980Ti嘅話火牛最少上RM550x<br />\n<br />\n第時upgrade,換CPU個步驟好繁複,又怕唔小心整到socket彎針<br />\n反而你顯示卡差少少,第時upgrade換過張,個步驟同換CPU比真係容易好多</blockquote><br />\n咁換做i7 7700<br />\nmb換Gigabyte GA-Z270-HD3 / z270 gaming 3<br />\n咁點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9636e7ff01540b97292a4102bc536fa20e48bd","tid":117372,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MB換Gigabyte GA-Z170X-UD5<br />\n或者Z170X gaming 5<br />\n呢兩塊o唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢兩塊板有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f867118a921c33f737f3bf12c2df0bf8914522c8","tid":117372,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你唔係買完要即刻用Hackintosh,可以全部都用新野<br />\n網上好似有人已經成功用Z270底板行Hackintosh,所以你可以睇下點做<br />\n<br />\n順便講,同樣咁多錢我會傾向選擇i7+GTX1060 6GB多過i5+GTX1070<br />\n因為打機i5 CPU好容易唔夠用,好多game已經食到4C8T<br />\nGTX1060 6GB反而多數人都覺得夠<br />\n再有錢可以i7+GTX1070<br />\n<br />\n如果你要買980Ti,去二手市場例如DCFever可能比較容易搵<br />\n用980Ti嘅話火牛最少上RM550x<br />\n<br />\n第時upgrade,換CPU個步驟好繁複,又怕唔小心整到socket彎針<br />\n反而你顯示卡差少少,第時upgrade換過張,個步驟同換CPU比真係容易好多</blockquote><br />\n咁換做i7 7700<br />\nmb換Gigabyte GA-Z270-HD3 / z270 gaming 3<br />\n咁點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果想上Z270,咁最好CPU直上7700K,RAM上埋DDR4-3000<br />\n再加雙排一體水冷/頂級雙塔風冷散熱,效能又高一截<br />\n否則你底板用返B250夠"}]}